'''Jarr''' is located at [[Shantay Pass]], just south of [[Al-Kharid]]. Players can begin the [[Desert Diary|Desert Diaries]] by speaking to him. He also awards players the [[Desert amulet]] for completing easy, medium, hard and elite tasks.
==Changes==
